    "course_title": "INTERPLAY BETWEEN MUSIC, ART, AND SOCIETY",
    "description": "Explore the relationships between the arts as they intersect with aspects of society, historically and in the present day, through various visual, auditory, and text-based expressive forms. Examine personal life experiences and ideas along with current issues related to music and art, and practice self-expression through the arts. No previous experience in any art form is necessary.",
